{"id": 1013, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在职场上见过哪些负能量？", "description": "出场自带低气压，办公室乌云密布。（题图来自：Elliot Freeman）", "record_count": 4073, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021839459LpAVQ7ay28kxCX4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-30T11:00:37Z", "options": [{"id": 94209, "content": "自带阴郁表情包。整天皱眉头。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641284}, {"id": 94210, "content": "做了半天的活 老板根本没仔细看甚至不看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 619391}, {"id": 94979, "content": "三天两头扬言不干了，可偏偏就是不见辞职。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643918}, {"id": 94212, "content": "其他合作部门，巨丑无比丑一女的，一说话跟所有人欠他钱一样。 看见她一整天都很烦躁。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640262}, {"id": 94214, "content": "“你懂我的意思么？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536887}, {"id": 94216, "content": "领导喜欢吹牛B~", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663204}, {"id": 94217, "content": "每天对你吐槽，希望你帮忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651576}, {"id": 94233, "content": "一起吃饭就是各种吐槽八卦", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319897}, {"id": 94237, "content": "老喊窮", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485485}, {"id": 94241, "content": "整天叨逼叨！对自己宽松对别人严格！喜欢以老卖老！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654140}, {"id": 94756, "content": "什么都不爱干，什么都干不好，总把活甩包在你身上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664807}, {"id": 81962, "content": "“名校毕业了不起啊”", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 81963, "content": "“我就是生错了时代”", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 94251, "content": "职场阴谋论", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 104159}, {"id": 81964, "content": "“这个报告随便搞搞好了，没人会看的”", "image": null, "praise_count": 381, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 94256, "content": "各种抱怨这个抱怨那个，错都在别人，却从没想过自己的问题！在部门之间倒是非！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630849}, {"id": 94014, "content": "旁边的同事整天唉声叹气。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 396, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662164}, {"id": 94016, "content": "表面对你推心置腹 实际上对你恨之入骨。", "image": null, "praise_count": 306, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662257}, {"id": 94208, "content": "一个每天和我抱怨要离职的同事 我离职了以后她屁颠屁颠的接着做了一年多⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663176}, {"id": 102913, "content": "欺负新员工", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370121}, {"id": 97794, "content": "领导不在high起来～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152720}, {"id": 94213, "content": "只招男性", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199459}, {"id": 94215, "content": "在全中心大会上中心最高领导是一边哭一边开会的，众脸懵逼~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663204}, {"id": 109328, "content": "上课聊游戏影响到老师及其他同学听课", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725248}, {"id": 94225, "content": "有事没事就到领导面前告黑状", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478703}, {"id": 94228, "content": "什么都不做，什么都觉得自己正确", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635941}, {"id": 94484, "content": "lbn到办公室的时候就感觉很压抑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473991}, {"id": 94234, "content": "太乱，没重点，明天再说，先睡!呵呵哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650032}, {"id": 94235, "content": "Aaacddadekdkdekdkxkdkxkdxmskxkdkkxskxkdkkxkdkddoodxkskkxdkxkodxkdkdkddxkddkdkkxskxkdkdkdkdkdkdkdoxkdxkkxkdkxdlxldldllldldllforodxkkrdkcdoxkxkskskxmdkdkkdkdxkdmxkekxkdkekxkdkskwowod", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183238gHTxbSM1OpQN3Rkt.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119625}, {"id": 94236, "content": "大家都这样，上淘宝聊微信", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603995}, {"id": 98332, "content": "非常努力的想插入其他人的聊天，结果让它说了三句话不到就要抱怨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680452}, {"id": 94238, "content": "同事之间 哪有真正的友谊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620569}, {"id": 94239, "content": "有拖延症的同事…天天追着他们屁股后面要材料", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403325}, {"id": 100639, "content": "圓滑的虛偽的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688332}, {"id": 94240, "content": "下班前务必反馈?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589192}, {"id": 94242, "content": "在做着自己不擅长的东西，挺吃力，但是在努力，哈哈给自己加些正能量", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654454}, {"id": 94499, "content": "东西无缘无故被偷或者被调包", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567133}, {"id": 94245, "content": "在单位里，女人多的地方就互相攀比，工作上溜须拍马屁。哼，鄙视??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663362}, {"id": 95013, "content": "没有目标的工作导致人的惰性发挥作用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664582}, {"id": 81959, "content": "“领导根本就不喜欢我啊，我努力有什么用”", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 94247, "content": "奖不明确，惩罚随意。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128904}, {"id": 81960, "content": "绷着脸，一开口就是和人争辩的情绪", "image": null, "praise_count": 313, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 94248, "content": "创业公司老板一不高兴情绪一上来就一言不发地退群了，等你发现后去问他只说他不想做了。WTF?!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589135}, {"id": 81961, "content": "“空降的？我凭什么让他管？他资格有我老吗？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 116, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 94249, "content": "反正这个月的KPI也完不成了，下班回家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 663393}, {"id": 94253, "content": "勾心斗角，爱打小报告，为了升迁无底线", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659821}, {"id": 94254, "content": "领导一给安排活 啊我真的特别忙做不了 仗着自己身材好 天天穿紧身衣 抖骚 随时请假 理由一大堆 啊我家厕所漏水了 我要去买瓷砖 我要回家给我老公做饭… 工作能力 没有 一出事儿使劲往别人头上推还被在群里当场戳穿  哎感觉这位大姐的事迹可以去豆瓣写个帖子了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589479}, {"id": 94255, "content": "能别人做的事情自己一定不做。WTF！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546267}, {"id": 94257, "content": "目前入职三年，经历的最大的负能量，2015年6月公司公布要加薪，到现在还没加！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 550790}, {"id": 94258, "content": "领导拖拖拉拉，说话难听", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150643}]}